longBusinessSummary: NovX21 Inc. operates an industrial prototype plant for the recovery of platinum group elements. It develops a patented chlorination technology to recover precious metals from recycled materials. The company was formerly known as Ressources Minières Pro-Or Inc. and changed its name to NovX21 Inc. in December 2014. NovX21 Inc. was founded in 1986 and is based in Montreal, Canada.
